snippet.title: Street Fighter 6 - M. Bison Update Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the M. Bison update now to welcome back the fallen dictator to Street Fighter 6!

👊 Fighting Ground - Play M. Bison's Combo Trials and Character Guide
✈️ World Tour - Meet the equestrian and increase your bond (if you dare)
🌐 Battle Hub - Use Psycho-powered moves in Avatar Battles

Time to put on a happy, and evil, face!

https://www.streetfighter.com/6/

#MBison #StreetFighter6 #Capcom
